com.adobe.acs.commons.httpcache.keys

Interface CacheKey


  • public interface CacheKey
    Generic CacheKey interface that allows multiple implementations of CacheKey's via CacheKeyFactories. All CacheKeys are scoped to being build off the Request object. Implementations are expected to override hashCode(), equals(Object), toString() methods.
